shoother_match_info:
You can also send results to PractiScore Competitor app from Safari web browser using browser 'Share' extension.

To change settings, switch between matches and search for the match results and other actions use the main app menu at the top right.

Use swipe left for more actions on various entries, including competitors, overall and stage results, matches, devices, etc.

Please report issues and email any questions at support@practiscore.com
